message: Dear Bob, I am delighted to present our exclusive product, which holds significant value for us at $15,000. Considering its worth to you at $12,000, I propose a fair transaction at $13,500. This price reflects a strategic midpoint, aiming to ensure both parties are satisfied with the deal. Should you have any questions or require further details, please don't hesitate to reach out. I look forward to your positive response and the opportunity to facilitate this transaction. Warm regards, Alice.
